&emsp;&emsp;然后是右键选中文字添加锚点按钮`rightside.pug`

```js
a.rightMenu-item(href="javascript:addAnchor();")
    script.
        function addAnchor () {
            if($("#no-anchor").length > 0){
                $("#no-anchor").remove();
            }
            var txt = window.getSelection().toString();
            txt = txt.replace(/<[^>]*>/g, "");
            $("#post-anchor-box").prepend('<a class="anchor-item" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="toAnchor(this)" data-pjax-state="">'+txt+'</a>');
            btf.snackbarShow("成功添加一个文本锚点");
        }
    i.fa.fa-book
    span='添加锚点'

```

&emsp;&emsp;当然没有右键就把js拿去，监听下选中文字后弹出个按钮触发一下`addAnchor()`就行。右键教程可看[自定义右键菜单](https://blog.dorakika.cn/p/20220118.html)

